baseimagestr:
Imagine this is your romantic partner, please remember this face.

In each trial, two faces will show up, please select the one that looks like your partner the most.

Press F to choose the left image, Press J to choose the right image

We have 5 practice trials for you to get familiar with the task. Press start to proceed when you are ready.
